{"wrapper":"div#el-blog-template","sections":{"blog-title":{"type":"blog-title","settings":{"color":"","blog-title":"WHAT TO WEAR WHEN YOU WORK FROM HOME","title_color":"","blog-title-font-size":42,"mobile-font-size":22,"alignment":"center"}},"1663872094552ff4cb":{"type":"custom-content-01","blocks":{"60fc0c85-ddcf-4402-bba2-ac04477bc5ac":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/What_to_wear_when_you_work_from_home_1_c294a9bb-887f-4961-a2aa-70a0c8f10f25.jpg","width":"100%","alignment":"center","image_alignment":"center"}},"1663872094b49339eb-0":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"","title_color":"#000000","title_font_size":20,"title_font_weight":400,"text":"<p>After more than a year of working from dining tables and home offices, it’s safe to say we’ve become accustomed to a relaxed way of dressing. Whilst many are excited to dust off their workplace attire, others are content with the prospect of permanently working within their own four walls.  <br\/><br\/>If working from home has moved from novelty to long-term reality, you may be considering giving your remote working wardrobe a freshen up. Here’s how…  <\/p>","content_color":"#000000","text_font_size":20,"margin_top":0,"border_top":0,"border_color":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":50,"width":"50%","alignment":"center","align_text":"left"}}},"block_order":["60fc0c85-ddcf-4402-bba2-ac04477bc5ac","1663872094b49339eb-0"],"settings":{"title":""}},"1663868435f0c44a9a":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"#000000","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>The ‘goes with everything’ knit<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/shirts-tops\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/shirts-tops\">T-shirt<\/a> coupled with jeans or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/shorts-trousers\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/shorts-trousers\">track pants<\/a> is a work from home outfit that covers all bases. To add a little something extra - one that confirms you haven’t just rolled out of bed - layer on a chunky knit. A classic button-down <a href=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/sweaters-cardigans\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/sweaters-cardigans\">cardigan<\/a> transitions easily from desk to evening and styles up your virtual meetings instantly.  <\/p>","text-color":"#000000","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/What_to_wear_when_you_work_from_home_2_d2108154-b78a-4ea8-ae23-58985c491534.png","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-left"}},"16638720430f34827e":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>The button-down shirt<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>Forgo your crisp, dry-clean-only shirts in favour of those more relaxed styles. Opt for pieces that can be machine washed and dried easily. White cotton shirts can wear their wrinkles well - if you’re not one to reach for an iron - and pair perfectly with jeans and slip-on shoes. Comfortable for running errands, yet smart for Zoom calls. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/What_to_wear_when_you_work_from_home_3_1bb243c2-9682-4668-922e-8880782b3f59.png","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-right"}},"166387328793cd4683":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>The easy-on shoe<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>It’s hard to feel like an outfit is complete without the right footwear. On the other hand, why don shoes when you have nowhere to go? You’re hardly going to slip into heels or boots for a day spent inside. If you’re someone who likes something between their feet and the floor, why not try a backless loafer? The perfect indoor shoe; comfortable yet functional. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/What_to_wear_when_you_work_from_home_4_95522edd-01b9-40b5-ab8f-23b849470205.png","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-left"}},"166387221970bc3eb0":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>The cropped trouser<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>If you haven’t worn ‘real’ trousers for more than a year, you certainly aren’t alone. Jeans and tailored pants have rapidly been replaced by leggings and joggers. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/shorts-trousers\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/shorts-trousers\">Cropped trousers<\/a> are our favourite in-between style. Just as comfy as loungewear, they still pair with your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/sweaters\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/sweaters\">sweaters<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/shirts-tops\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/shirts-tops\">T-shirts<\/a>, but give you a more pulled-together look. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/What_to_wear_when_you_work_from_home_5.png","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-right"}},"f82e9674-462e-405d-abe8-0768e14e9810":{"type":"blog-two-grid","settings":{"grid-title":"","grid-title-font-size":35,"title-margin-bottom":20,"grid-title-color":"","content-alignment":"center","grid-content":"<p><em><strong>The floaty dress<\/strong><\/em> <br\/><br\/>If you feel like a change from loungewear, a floaty spring dress is the perfect way to lift your spirits; they are one of our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/blogs\/journal\/your-8-spring-wardrobe-essentials\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/blogs\/journal\/your-8-spring-wardrobe-essentials\">spring wardrobe essentials<\/a> for a reason. Sometimes a change of routine is needed - why not designate one day a week to switch up your work from home attire? A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/dresses-skirts\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/dresses-skirts\">midi dress<\/a> that’s loose-fitting enough for working from home, yet you can still meet your friends for after-work drinks is a great idea. Swap your slides for heels and you’ll be on your way. <\/p>","text-color":"","grid-image-picker":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/What_to_wear_when_you_work_from_home_6.png","image-caption":"","grid-swap":"grid-left"}},"b98148d7-cae6-42da-b04d-56e6e5daed1b":{"type":"custom-content-01","blocks":{"template--14591016108134__b98148d7-cae6-42da-b04d-56e6e5daed1b-1686142328a994a513-0":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"Talk about your brand","title_color":"#000000","title_font_size":35,"title_font_weight":400,"text":"","content_color":"#000000","text_font_size":25,"margin_top":30,"border_top":1,"border_color":"","padding_top":30,"padding_bottom":30,"width":"50%","alignment":"center","align_text":"left"}},"template--14591016108134__b98148d7-cae6-42da-b04d-56e6e5daed1b-1686142328a994a513-1":{"type":"image","disabled":true,"settings":{"width":"50%","alignment":"center","image_alignment":"center"}},"a088c57c-ac2c-486a-adae-1cd9241f0b6d":{"type":"cta","settings":{"padding-top":24,"title":"Shop Essentials","url":"https:\/\/www.chintiandparker.com\/collections\/cashmere-essentials","title_color":"#000000","title_font_size":32,"cta_bg":"","cta_border_color":"","cta_border":1,"align_text":"center"}}},"block_order":["template--14591016108134__b98148d7-cae6-42da-b04d-56e6e5daed1b-1686142328a994a513-0